  "detailed_description": "<strong>Lord Of Tower is an action game where you go up a tower and enjoy battles with various bosses.<br>The boss has a unique pattern and will not be easy to defeat.<br>Beat the bosses who are the owners of each floor and become the true lord of the tower!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Battle with the boss</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/2438d3bfe981e0c9bd6ea8072cf4f694.poster.avif?t=1714694665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/2438d3bfe981e0c9bd6ea8072cf4f694.webm?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/2438d3bfe981e0c9bd6ea8072cf4f694.mp4?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You will face bosses with patterns that stimulate your desire to win.</li></ul></strong><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Master the boss's pattern and win the battle!</li></ul></strong><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keep challenging endlessly to conquer the tower!</li></ul></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Four types of characters</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/cfe54a4b2aab61abb4f4540ad381eca7.poster.avif?t=1714694665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/cfe54a4b2aab61abb4f4540ad381eca7.webm?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/cfe54a4b2aab61abb4f4540ad381eca7.mp4?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can meet characters with different charms.</li></ul></strong><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can experience a variety of combat encounters.</li></ul></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Growth system</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/d20bbfbede53b39a1f9c639f0319dc6b.poster.avif?t=1714694665\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/d20bbfbede53b39a1f9c639f0319dc6b.webm?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2909200/extras/d20bbfbede53b39a1f9c639f0319dc6b.mp4?t=1714694665\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Keep growing through equipment collection and skill acquisition.</li></ul></strong><br><strong><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>As you grow, you can experience more spectacular battles.</li></ul></strong>",
